(3, 'TOPIC00220231104093716', 'SUBTOPIC00420231104105229', 'VIDEO00320231104115723', 'INTRODUCTION TO PROGRESSION', '<p>At the end of this video, student should be able to understand the following objectives;</p>\r\n<p>1. Defination of Progression</p>\r\n<p>2. Types of Progression</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 32px; line-height: 40px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Progression</h1>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">A progression (which is also known as a sequence) is nothing but a pattern of numbers. For example, 3, 6, 9, 12, ... is a progression because there is a pattern observed where every number here is obtained by adding 3 to its previous number. But this pattern doesn\'t need to be the same in every progression.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">The pattern of a progression depends on its type. Let us see the types of progressions along with examples and their formulas.</p>\r\n<div id=\"a\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: #000000; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<div id=\"circle\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; margin: 0px 0px -15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; position: relative; top: 10px; left: -5px; height: 40px; width: 40px; border-radius: 50%; z-index: 0; background-color: #e1fff6;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: left !important; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); position: relative;\">What is the Definition of a Progression?</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important;\">Progression</strong>&nbsp;is a list of numbers (or items) that exhibit a particular pattern. A progression is also known as a sequence. In a progression, every term is obtained by applying a specific rule on its previous term. In other words, every term of a progression is defined by a general term (or) n<sup style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: small; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: super;\">th</sup>&nbsp;term, which is denoted by a<sub style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; bottom: -0.25em;\">n</sub>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">For example, the n<sup style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: small; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: super;\">th</sup>&nbsp;term of a progression 3, 5, 7, 9, ... is a<sub style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; bottom: -0.25em;\">n</sub>&nbsp;= 2n + 1. Substituting n = 1, 2, 3, ... here, we get the 1<sup style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: small; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: super;\">st</sup>, 2<sup style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: small; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: super;\">nd</sup>, 3<sup style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: small; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: super;\">rd</sup>, .... terms. For example:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; color: #000000; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside disc; color: #333333;\">When n = 1, first term = 2(1) + 1 = 3.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside disc; color: #333333;\">When n = 2, second term = 2(2) + 1 = 5.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside disc; color: #333333;\">When n = 3, third term = 2(3) + 1 = 7<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important;\" />and so on.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div id=\"b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: #000000; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<div id=\"circle\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; margin: 0px 0px -15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; position: relative; top: 10px; left: -5px; height: 40px; width: 40px; border-radius: 50%; z-index: 0; background-color: #e1fff6;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: left !important; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); position: relative;\">Types of Progressions</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">There are mainly 3 types of progressions in math. They are:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; color: #000000; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside disc; color: #333333;\">Arithmetic Progression (AP)</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside disc; color: #333333;\">Geometric Progression (GP)</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside disc; color: #333333;\">Harmonic Progression (HP)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; width: 400px;\" src=\"https://d138zd1ktt9iqe.cloudfront.net/media/seo_landing_files/types-of-progressions-1646371090.png\" alt=\"Progressions\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Each type of progression along with a simple definition and example is tabulated below.</p>\r\n<table style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; background: #fff7db; border-radius: 4px; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12); table-layout: fixed; width: 544px; color: #000000; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<thead style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; background: #ffe896;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important;\">\r\n<th style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; padding: 12px 9px 12px 15px; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word;\" scope=\"col\">Progression</th>\r\n<th style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; padding: 12px 9px 12px 15px; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word;\" scope=\"col\">Definition</th>\r\n<th style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; padding: 12px 9px 12px 15px; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word;\" scope=\"col\">Example</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; padding: 12px 9px 12px 15px; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arithmetic Progression (AP)</td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; padding: 12px 9px 12px 15px; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">The differences between any two consecutive numbers are all same.</td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; padding: 12px 9px 12px 15px; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">1, 4, 7, 10, ...</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; padding: 12px 9px 12px 15px; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Geometric Progression (GP)</td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; padding: 12px 9px 12px 15px; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">The ratios of any two consecutive numbers are all same.</td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; padding: 12px 9px 12px 15px; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">4, 16, 64, 256, ...</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; padding: 12px 9px 12px 15px; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Harmonic Progression (HP)</td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; padding: 12px 9px 12px 15px; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">The reciprocals of terms form an AP.</td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; padding: 12px 9px 12px 15px; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">1/2, 1/4, 1/6, ...</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">We will learn about each progression in detail in the upcoming sections.</p>\r\n<div id=\"c\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: #000000; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<div id=\"circle\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; margin: 0px 0px -15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; position: relative; top: 10px; left: -5px; height: 40px; width: 40px; border-radius: 50%; z-index: 0; background-color: #e1fff6;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: left !important; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); position: relative;\">Arithmetic Progression</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">An&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: #01a5f2;\" href=\"https://www.cuemath.com/algebra/arithmetic-progressions/\">arithmetic progression</a>&nbsp;(AP) is a sequence of numbers in which each successive term is the&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: #01a5f2;\" href=\"https://www.cuemath.com/numbers/sum/\">sum</a>&nbsp;of its preceding term and a fixed number. This fixed number is called the common difference. For example, 1, 4, 7, 10, ... is an AP as every number is obtained by adding a fixed number 3 to its previous term.</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; color: #000000; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside disc; color: #333333;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important;\">2<sup style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: small; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: super;\">nd</sup>&nbsp;term</strong>&nbsp;= 4 = 1 + 3&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important;\">= 1<sup style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: small; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: super;\">st</sup>&nbsp;term + 3</strong></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside disc; color: #333333;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important;\">3<sup style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: small; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: super;\">rd</sup>&nbsp;term&nbsp;</strong>= 7 = 4 + 3&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important;\">= 2<sup style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: small; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: super;\">nd</sup>&nbsp;term + 3</strong></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside disc; color: #333333;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important;\">4<sup style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: small; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: super;\">th</sup>&nbsp;term</strong>&nbsp;= 10 = 7 + 3&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important;\">= 3<sup style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: small; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: super;\">rd</sup>&nbsp;term + 3</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important;\" />and so on.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">In general, an arithmetic progression looks like this:</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; width: 400px;\" src=\"https://d138zd1ktt9iqe.cloudfront.net/media/seo_landing_files/arithmetic-progression-1646371064.png\" alt=\"Arithmetic Progression\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Here,</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; color: #000000; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside disc; color: #333333;\">\'a\' is the first term and</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside disc; color: #333333;\">\'d\' is the common difference (fixed number)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold !important; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative !important; color: #000000; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Arithmetic Progression Example</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">For example, Minnie put $30 in her piggy bank when she was 7 years old. She increased the amount she put in her piggy bank on each successive birthday by $3. So, the amount in her piggy bank follows the pattern of $30, $33, $36, and so on. The succeeding terms are obtained by adding a fixed number, that is, $3. This fixed number is called the common difference (It can be positive, negative, or zero). Hence the progression 30, 33, 36, ... is an AP.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold !important; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative !important; color: #000000; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Arithmetic Progression Formulas</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Let the first term of the progression be a, the common difference be d, and the n<sup style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: small; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: super;\">th</sup>&nbsp;term be a<sub style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; bottom: -0.25em;\">n</sub>. Then, the arithmetic progression formulas are given by:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-se