 text-decoration: none; color: #01a5f2;\" href=\"https://www.cuemath.com/algebra/sum-of-an-infinite-gp/\">Sum of infinite geometric series</a>, S<sub style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; bottom: -0.25em;\">&infin;</sub>&nbsp;= a / (1 - r) when |r| &lt; 1 and S<sub style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; bottom: -0.25em;\">&infin;</sub>&nbsp;diverges when |r| &ge; 1.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; width: 400px;\" src=\"https://d138zd1ktt9iqe.cloudfront.net/media/seo_landing_files/geometric-progression-formulas-1646371150.png\" alt=\"Geometric progression formulas\" /></p>\r\n<div id=\"e\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: #000000; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<div id=\"circle\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font: inherit; margin: 0px 0px -15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; position: relative; top: 10px; left: -5px; height: 40px; width: 40px; border-radius: 50%; z-index: 0; background-color: #e1fff6;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: left !important; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); position: relative;\">Harmonic Progression</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">A&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: #01a5f2;\" href=\"https://www.cuemath.com/numbers/harmonic-progression/\">harmonic progression</a>&nbsp;is a sequence obtained by taking the&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: #01a5f2;\" href=\"https://www.cuemath.com/numbers/reciprocal-definition/\">reciprocal</a>&nbsp;of the terms of an arithmetic progression. The sequence of&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: #01a5f2;\" href=\"https://www.cuemath.com/numbers/natural-numbers/\">natural numbers</a>&nbsp;is an arithmetic progression. So, taking reciprocals of each term we get 1,1/2,1/3,1/4,... This is harmonic progression.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold !important; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative !important; color: #000000; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Harmonic Progression Example</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">When a ball is dropped, the initial height reached by the ball is 1/2 units and after the first impact, the height attained by the ball is 1/4 units. After the second impact, the height attained by the ball is 1/6 units. After the third impact, the height attained by the ball is 1/8 units, and so on. Now the sequence of heights formed by the ball is: 1/2, 1/4, 1/6, 1/8, ...</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding: 2px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px !important; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">This&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Untitled Sans\', sans-serif !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: #01a5f2;\" href=\"https://www.cuemath.com/sequences-and-series-formulas/\">sequence</a>&nbsp;is a harmonic progression because t